      "logical_unit_id": "MD12963_lu8",
      "document_id": "MD12963",
      "title": "Chapter II - Grant of No Objection Certificate (NOC) / Approval by RBI ..................... 4",
      "text": "Chapter II - Grant of No Objection Certificate (NOC) / Approval by RBI ..................... 4\n<image>\nIn exercise of the powers conferred by Section 45K, 45L, and 45M of the\nReserve Bank of India Act, 1934 and all other provisions / laws enabling the Reserve\nBank of India ('RBI') in this regard, RBI being satisfied that it is necessary and\nexpedient in the public interest so to do, hereby issues the Directions hereinafter\nspecified.",
