      "logical_unit_id": "MD12963_lu10",
      "document_id": "MD12963",
      "title": "A. Short Title and Commencement",
      "text": "A. Short Title and Commencement\n1.\nThese Directions shall be called the Reserve Bank of India (Non-Banking\nFinancial Companies - Voluntary Amalgamation) Directions, 2025.\n2.\nThese Directions shall come into force with immediate effect.",
